<p>To unsubscribe or to change your personal details or subscription choices, please click here, to log in and go to your account settings , or click inside any e-mail communication from us to &ldquo;manage your preferences.&rdquo; You can also send an e-mail to unsubscribe@mohawkpaper.com to be opted out of all marketing communications. 
Felt and Wire Shop customers can unsubscribe by e-mailing help@feltandwireshop.com.  
</p>
    
 <h4>Changes to This Privacy Policy</h4>   

<p>Mohawk reserves the right to modify or supplement this policy at any time. If a material change to this policy is made, Mohawk Fine Papers Inc. will post a notice on its home page, and any changes to the policy will be posted on this page. If you have additional questions regarding security you can e-mail customerservice@mohawkpaper.com
</p>
    
